LAHORE, Mar 17 (APP): Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif Sunday here held a meeting with leader of Pakistan Muslim League (N) Khawaja Saad Rafique.
Khawaja Saad congratulated the prime minister on assuming his office and expressed best wishes for him. During the meeting, they discussed the overall political situation in the country and matters of mutual interest.
